		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row1"><span class="name"><a name="40209"></a><b>Diox</b></span><br /><span class="postdetails">Magician<br /><br /><br />Joined: 08 Mar 2003<br />Posts: 19<br /></span><br /></td>
